<problem id="fs-idp55794496">
<para id="fs-idp55794752">What is the effect on the concentration of ammonia, hydroxide ion, and ammonium ion when the following are added to a basic buffer solution of equal concentrations of ammonia and ammonium nitrate:</para>
<para id="fs-idp70891616">(a) KI</para>
<para id="fs-idp55795008">(b) NH<sub>3</sub></para>
